&lt;p&gt;We are seeking to appoint an enthusiastic team player to join our friendly and dynamic Colorectal Surgical Unit at Dorset County Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The appointee will join the surgical team providing specialist Colorectal and general surgical services to the population of West Dorset and the adjoining areas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will join a 1 in 7 on call rota for general surgery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We can offer you a wide variety of trust and NHS based benefits, but also, we can offer you a place in a friendly team with strong team spirit working to meet individual, team and trust goals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applications from those wishing to work less than full time would be considered.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameMr Ben StubbsJob titleColorectal ConsultantAdditional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact Mr Ben Stubbs, Colorectal Consultant via Suzy Evans, Medical Secretary on 01305 255934&lt;/p&gt;
